history.content:
Hello- congrats on your upcoming graduation! If you're on the degree list, you can take fewer than 12 units. If you have financial aid, you will want to be in at least 6 units. Either way, you should let your ESS adviser know what your plans are and make sure that you do a final degree check. Congrats again!

If you're an international student or student athlete, you will need to check in with BIO or the ASC respectively.
